<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākābdē nidhiratnabhānugaṇitē caitryāṁ ravērvvāsarē
<lb n="2"/>śrīsiṁhyācalanāyakasya nṛhārēḥ prādātprasūnasrajaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> cātu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rtthyānvayasiṁdhuśītakiraṇō <unclear>bha</unclear>ktyā svadēvīyutō śrīviśvēśva
<lb n="4" break="no"/>radēvabhūpatilaka<unclear>ḥ</unclear> svābhīṣṭasaṁsiddhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbu
<lb n="5" break="no"/>lu 1299 gunēṁṭi caitra punnamiyu ravivāramunāṁḍu
<lb n="6"/>śrī sarvvalōkāśrayacakravarttulaina śrīvi<unclear>ṣṇu</unclear>varddhana viśvēśva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>radēvarājulu tamakunnu tama dē<unclear>vulu</unclear> manumayya
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁgārikiṁ<unclear>ni</unclear> puṇyamugānu śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuniki nityamu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>nnu Oka tirumāla cāti<unclear>ṁ</unclear>panu Ayidu māḍalaku kuṁca
<lb n="10" break="no"/>prasādamu tāmava<unclear>ṭṭi</unclear>paḍudāsari Alluṁḍu pūrā(I)yi
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ki<unclear>nni</unclear> peṭṭenu Ītaṁḍu Ī prasādamu bhujiṁci nityamu
<lb n="12" break="no"/>nnu Oka tirumāla māpuṭi dhūpaAvusarāna peṭṭa
<lb n="13" break="no"/><unclear>ṁ</unclear>galāṁḍu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmamu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśrī
<lb n="14"/>śrīśrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> tōṁṭagaṭṭu varada<unclear>yaṁ</unclear>gāricē vilici Icina
<lb n="15"/>viśvēśvaradēvarājulu tamaku tama dēvulu manu
<lb n="16" break="no"/>marudrayaṁgāriki puṇyaṁgā nityamu ṟēpa<supplied reason="omitted">ṭi</supplied> tiruma<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="17" break="no"/>jenamu kuṁḍaṁḍu teci peṭṭu Appanaṁbhaḷa Allu
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ṁḍu vallabha<unclear>nma</unclear>ku Ayudu māḍalu peṭṭiri 5
<lb n="19"/>padmanidimāḍalu <unclear>reṁḍu</unclear> taṁbaku <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> I prasāda
<lb n="20" break="no"/>naku śrīśrīśrī
</p>

